  "issue_title": "test: add offline validation checklist and tests",
  "issue_body": "## Problem\n\nMilestone 2 needs offline validation to prove the hybrid local core works without cloud models or hosted routing.\n\nThe milestone should not be considered complete until representative local-only flows pass.\n\n## Proposed behavior\n\nAdd an offline validation checklist and tests for Milestone 2 flows:\n\n- `Hello`\n- `Help`\n- `Open Settings`\n- `Go back`\n- one ambiguous request routed through the local-model-needed path\n\nValidation should confirm intent gate behavior, event emission, deterministic fallback, and policy/tool routing where applicable.\n\n## User workflow\n\nA developer or tester should be able to run the app offline and validate the key Milestone 2 flows without configuring a cloud provider, API key, or backend service.\n\n## Local-first impact\n\nThis proves the product direction: TouchPilot's core agent behavior works locally.\n\n## Safety and security considerations\n\nOffline validation should include at least one blocked or approval-related event path if practical, to confirm local policy remains active.\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n\n- [ ] Add a Milestone 2 offline validation checklist.\n- [ ] Validate `Hello` locally.\n- [ ] Validate `Help` locally.\n- [ ] Validate `Open Settings` locally.\n- [ ] Validate `Go back` locally.\n- [ ] Validate one ambiguous local-model-needed request.\n- [ ] Confirm each flow emits expected agent events.\n- [ ] Confirm no cloud provider/API key/backend is required.\n- [ ] Add automated tests where practical and document any manual live-test steps.\n",
